data.text:
Three Blind Dates

Frasier's clinginess drives everyone crazy and they try to set him up with various women.

Dead Zone

The body of a man involved in recovering sunken treasure is discovered pinned to the wall of his new cabin cruiser by a bloody spear fired from a speargun at close range.

The New Girl

Transfer student Tori is introduced in this episode, but Zack and Tori don't hit it off, and they are paired up for an ad project. Lisa alienates the Dance Committee before the Fall Ball.

Slater's Sister

Slater's sister J.B. comes to town to visit and Zack wants to date her. Slater tries to put a stop to it and it almost ruins his relationship with both Zack and his sister.
